is bred into you people.

346
00:23:18.172 --> 00:23:20.137
I've had enough of your shit.

347
00:23:21.275 --> 00:23:21.586
Let me tell you something...

348
00:23:25.758 --> 00:23:27.413
When those cattle
walked onto our land.

349
00:23:27.517 --> 00:23:30.379
