351
00:23:37.620 --> 00:23:39.172
Son of a bitch.

352
00:23:39.275 --> 00:23:43.241
♪

353
00:23:43.344 --> 00:23:44.586
Back up.

354
00:23:44.689 --> 00:23:46.827
You should respect
your veterans.

355
00:24:04.689 --> 00:24:06.517
Boy. you sure made
a mess of this.

356
00:24:06.620 --> 00:24:09.000
It was a mess
when I got here.

357
00:24:10.379 --> 00:24:11.758
