with a straight face. Ben.

362
00:24:29.586 --> 00:24:32.551
Cattle wandered
onto res land. John.

363
00:24:32.655 --> 00:24:34.379
Yeah. well.

364
00:24:34.482 --> 00:24:35.241
cattle don't know
the difference

365
00:24:35.344 --> 00:24:36.931
