of the brave ♪

389
00:26:23.517 --> 00:26:25.310
Ladies and gentlemen.
I'd like to welcome you out

390
00:26:25.413 --> 00:26:26.931
to the 2018

391
00:26:27.034 --> 00:26:29.000
Greater Montana
Livestock Auction.

392
00:26:29.103 --> 00:26:30.689
