not to him.

423
00:27:51.241 --> 00:27:52.655
Please.

424
00:27:55.172 --> 00:27:56.241
Please.

425
00:28:00.586 --> 00:28:02.068
We're gonna do this my way.
all right?

426
00:28:02.172 --> 00:28:04.275
You understand? My way.
Yeah.

427
00:28:04.379 --> 00:28:05.793
