434
00:28:20.862 --> 00:28:21.689
I couldn't hit it
if he didn't tee it up.

435
00:28:21.793 --> 00:28:24.551
and my offer
still stands. John.

436
00:28:24.655 --> 00:28:26.068
Yeah. well...

437
00:28:26.172 --> 00:28:28.758
